data.description:
Introducing Aurora Shores' Waterfront Gem in the delightful little area called Reminderville! Nestled along the serene canal, this inviting 4-bedroom, 2-bath abode boasts a spacious open layout and recent upgrades including a new drive, furnace, roof, new dock and sleek stainless steel appliances. Step outside to your private dock and soak in the captivating waterfront vistas. Community amenities abound with 2 pools, playgrounds, and a rentable banquet room at the marina clubhouse. Fresh paint, sealed windows, and modern finishes ensure a tranquil haven for relaxed living. Embrace the allure of waterfront living – your dream retreat awaits!
305 acre private lake for swimming, fishing, boating & water skiing. 2 inground heated pools, 2 soft sand beaches, slalom course, 2 playgrounds, 4 tennis/pickleball courts, 2 basketball courts, volleyball court, baseball diamond, marina & party center!
